{"type": "article", "id": 4293, "title": "自行车挂架 Pincher", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-11T07:46:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233259IOuo9BMscX6LedWR.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自瑞典的建筑师 Karl Mikael Ling 日前推出了他的最新设计作品 Pincher 。这是一款构造简洁优雅的自行车挂架，仅由一个弯曲的钢质挂架、一块铝质面板以及一个螺丝构成。使用时，只需将挂架和铝板用螺丝固定在墙面上即可。Karl Mikael Ling 为 Pincher 施以陶瓷质感的磨砂涂层，而在挂架与自行车需要接触的部位，设计师还为其配置了工业级聚氨酯软垫，防止自行车被挂出划痕。整个挂架小巧精致，最大可承重 30 千克，定价 80 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.karlmikaelling.com/store/pincher\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233256SXhrc4mkHzYvM8Us.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233257xB4JqkAKfTsymtr3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052332576NEtk1ozunbJxvg0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052332584drnP5kz12Fy8WhR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}